text:
{
  "prompt": "A detailed render of an electric bicycle frame with a 48V 60Ah battery pack inserted into the downtube. The battery is shaped to match the contour of the downtube, which is thickened to accommodate it. The frame is step-through type, with a white and black color scheme. The bike features a mid-drive motor and rear air suspension. The battery has a visible seam or latch area for removal, and wiring is neatly routed along the left side of the frame. The image is side-view, with clean lighting and a mechanical engineering style of illustration.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A clean 3D-rendered image of a classic Honda Super Cub frame only, without any body panels, engine, or wheels. The frame is metallic silver, showing its tubular steel structure with the characteristic step-through design. It is displayed on a light gray background, in side view, with detailed welds, mounting points, and open areas for rear suspension and engine brackets. The lighting is even and soft, with a sharp focus on the structural lines of the frame.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic electric motorcycle with a sleek, PCX125-style body design, featuring a skateboard-style flat chassis. The battery pack is integrated into the flat floorboard under the rider’s feet, emphasizing a low center of gravity. The motorcycle has a step-through frame, front and rear suspension, large on-road tires, disc brakes, and a compact hub motor on the rear wheel. The design is modern, aerodynamic, and suitable for urban commuting. The background is neutral and minimal to highlight the vehicle.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A detailed 3D rendering of a PCX-style electric scooter without body panels or fairings, exposing the internal frame, battery pack in a skateboard-style underfloor position, suspension components, electric motor, wiring, and controller. The frame is matte black, with visible weld joints, aluminum swingarm, and center stand. The setting is a clean, neutral studio background with soft lighting.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution 3D render of a modern electric scooter frame without any outer body panels (no cowling). The exposed structure includes a central flat battery pack mounted on a skateboard-style platform, visible wiring, a central motor mount beneath the seat, front suspension forks, rear swingarm with shocks, and disc brakes. The frame is minimalistic and industrial, shown in matte steel gray against a light gray background, with excellent detail and clarity.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic side view of an electric motorcycle with a naked, minimalist design and no fairings (cowlings). The frame is open and exposes the battery system in a flat skateboard-style layout beneath the rider's feet. The vehicle features a central aluminum frame, a low-slung wide battery pack along the bottom, mid-mounted foot pegs, and standard motorcycle wheels. The front includes a round LED headlight and inverted fork suspension, while the rear has a dual shock absorber setup. Everything is matte black, set against a neutral gray studio background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A side view technical illustration of an electric motorcycle with a skateboard-style chassis, where the battery is mounted flat and wide under the rider's feet, integrated into the floorboard like a skateboard deck. The frame is minimal and exposed, with a low center of gravity. The front suspension is telescopic, the rear has dual shocks, and the wheels are mid-size with disc brakes. The battery pack is rectangular and flat, occupying the entire under-deck space. The handlebars are flat and clean. No fairings or body panels are present. Drawn in clean, realistic style with light shadows on a neutral background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic side-view render of an electric motorcycle with a minimalist, exposed frame and no outer fairings. The design features a skateboard-style flat battery pack integrated into the entire bottom platform area (skateboard layout), creating a low center of gravity. The motorcycle has large road tires, disc brakes, a visible rear suspension, a central motor, and a matte black tubular frame. Set against a neutral studio background with no distractions.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution 3D-rendered image of a modern electric motorcycle with a central mid-drive motor clearly visible beneath the frame. The motorcycle features a minimalistic design with no fairings, matte black tubular frame, round LED headlight, alloy wheels, rear suspension, and a large flat skateboard-style battery pack mounted at the bottom of the frame. The setting is a neutral studio background with soft lighting emphasizing the components.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A sleek, minimalist electric motorcycle in a 3D-rendered side view, featuring a completely removed top tube for a clean, open-frame design. The motorcycle is matte black with a skateboard-style flat battery pack mounted low between the wheels. The seat floats above the frame, supported by rear shocks. Central motor and drive chain are exposed, and the bike has alloy wheels, a round LED headlight, and a clean modern look without any plastic fairings. Background is a neutral light gray.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital rendering of a minimalist electric motorcycle designed around a single diagonal downtube extending from the head tube. The matte black steel frame features no top tube. The large rectangular battery is mounted low along the downtube, flush with the bottom frame rail. A compact mid-drive electric motor is integrated at the crank area. The motorcycle includes sleek black alloy wheels, disc brakes, dual rear shocks, a flat seat, and clean cable routing. The background is a soft neutral gray, emphasizing the structure and simplicity of the motorcycle.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution image of a minimalist electric motorcycle featuring only a single diagonal downtube extending from the headtube to the lower motor mount, forming the structural backbone. The motorcycle has no top tube, creating an open triangle frame. The motor is centrally located, and a slim, elongated battery is mounted below the downtube. The motorcycle is matte black with clean lines, mid-sized wheels, and disc brakes, set against a neutral gray background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
